<section class="about-value">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="title-bold text-center">Get to know us</div>
    <h2 class="text-center">About Us</h2>
    <hr>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-6 large-offset-1 columns">
      <div class="title-bold m-margin">Our Values</div>
      <p><strong>We believe every human being deserves a life of joy and happiness, yet as we all know from our own experience joyful occurrence is a rarity in our culture.</strong></p>
      <p class="gray">It is truly our desire to give you a piece of happiness you deserve by turning one of your dreams into reality. A dream every girl has been dreaming since a very young age, a dream of the perfect proposal.</p>
      <p class="gray l-margin">We understand the numerous challenges in creating an unforgettable experience for your love ones and that is the reason why we exist; we make your dream come to life. We will guide you in executing a perfectly genuine gesture that not only will put her on cloud nine but also provokes envy compassions from others. A dream proposal identified with joyous envy.</p>

    </div>
    <div class="large-5 end columns">
      <div class="title-bold m-margin">Our Role</div>
      <p class="gray">A proposal needs to be carefully premeditated and planned; not only it is time consuming but also painstaking. Planning a proposal should be an enjoyable experience for everyone involved. Therefore our primary role is to assist and facilitate the whole planning process thus making your life less stressful than it already is.</p>
      <p class="gray">You only have one chance to make this proposal thoughtful and memorable, it is one of the many ways to show how much she means to you, and if you execute it perfectly it will be one of the most memorable experiences in her life. We are here to smooth the process in order for you to pull off the proposal envy of her life.</p>
      <p><strong>Your compassionate effort will reward itself when she says yes.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

