<section class="about-why">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="title-bold text-center white">We Plan, You Pop The Question</div>
    <h2 class="text-center white">Why Hire Us?</h2>
    <hr>
    {% for reason in post.get_field('reasons') %}
      <div class="reason small-12 medium-6 end columns">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="small-12 medium-3 end columns small-only-text-center text-right">
            <img class="reason-img" src="{{TimberImage(reason.icon).src}}" />
          </div>
          <div class="small-12 medium-9 large-7 xlarge-7 end columns small-only-text-center">
            <div class="title-bold white s-margin">{{reason.title}}</div>
            <p class="white">{{reason.description}}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="no-padding">
  <div class="row max-width handy">

  <div class="large-5 large-offset-2 white-panel columns">
      <div class="title-bold s-margin">Founder</div>
      <h3 class="m-margin">Handy Lu</h3>
      <hr>
      <p class="gray">Coming from experience at startups, agencies, and full-time freelance, Alexander’s process is limber and eclectic. Inspired by Sci-Fi movies, Eastern philosophy, and well-made espresso, he works for a beautiful, informed future. He sees each new project as an opportunity to grow in effectiveness and understanding, and is a true proponent of friendship as a means to better building.</p>
  </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row max-width arista">
  <div class="large-5 large-offset-5 white-panel columns">
      <div class="title-bold s-margin">Co-founder</div>
      <h3 class="m-margin">Arista Tjandra Widjaja</h3>
      <hr>
      <p class="gray">Arista is driven by a constant desire to learn more and build better, while carrying a firm resolution to never act too grown-up. With years of interactive and illustration background, everything he does is meticulous yet imaginative. Known for keeping his cool in tough-goings, Mike remains a solid-pillar in the foundation of our studio’s positive attitude and steadfast approach.</p>
  </div>
  </div>

</section>

